{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>BallMan</i> is a smiley round creature who likes to spend its days rolling around the world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But suddenly, during the year<i> 1994</i>, something weird happened and several bad creatures called <i>BadBalls</i> appeared, messing up BallMan's life. <i>Make BallMan's world free again!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Guide it through 7 different levels, such caves, countryside and more, helping it clean up its world while enjoying the awesome old school MIDI soundtrack and the funny animations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge yourself and the other players making the highest score on the scoreboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a <strong>real </strong>arcade game where you have to insert coins to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">...of course you don't have to actually insert coins into your PC :) Read the control list below for further information.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Default controls:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Up arrow -&gt; Climb ladder up, look upwards</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Down arrow -&gt; Climb ladder down, look downwards, crouch</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Left arrow -&gt; Roll to the left</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Right arrow -&gt; Roll to the right</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>N -&gt; Jump</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>M -&gt; Fire  </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>C -&gt; Insert coin</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game managing:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>P -&gt; Pause the game</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Esc -&gt; Pause and go windowed mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>0 -&gt; Fullscreen mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>1 -&gt; Windowed (small)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2 -&gt; Windowed (medium)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3 -&gt; Windowed (large) </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Everyone can enjoy BallMan!\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why? Because it's only a <strong>few megabytes </strong>in size and you will download it in a couple of seconds!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also, you <strong>don't need </strong>a thousand dollars gaming PC to run it, your grandma's old laptop will be more than enough to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">...true story, tested by myself ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Have fun, and follow me for new releases!</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Boot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/391bcc12a171db453229108d630d2efd82974e03.jpg"},{"name":"Bouncing around","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/c9a23b62e1fde65e5bdc96e03a945dbd9a8f0289.jpg"},{"name":"5 Minutes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/e83b453cf8b8453f4bf9ecf61450c51a6121406a.jpg"},{"name":"10 Minutes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/ad6076830301d3050035a25a3fef6c8b16510899.jpg"},{"name":"Half an Hour","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/611f0d5c688a24716a579429230b5504a13fbe37.jpg"},{"name":"A whole Hour!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/1176c576cc2c254efac395e5365eff3a58c51cc5.jpg"},{"name":"Like a Soccer match","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3256630/31f2f5